@startuml
autonumber
title User Login Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Auth API" as API
database "UserDB" as DB

User -> UI : Enter Email/Pass
UI -> API : POST /login
API -> DB : Find User
DB --> API : User Data
API -> API : Validate Password

alt success
    API --> UI : 200 OK (Token)
    UI -> User : Redirect to Home
else failure
    API --> UI : 401 Unauthorized
    UI -> User : Show Error Message
end
@enduml